('Wish You Were Here', 'Pink Floyd', 'Storm Thorgerson', 'Photography', 1975, 'Harvest', ARRAY['Rock'], 'Two businessmen shaking hands, one on fire — Thorgerson''s surrealist comment on the music industry remains searingly relevant.', '0bCAjiUamIFqKJsekOYuRw', 210, 40, 50, '[]', 'approved'),
