('In Rainbows', 'Radiohead', 'Stanley Donwood', 'Illustration', 2007, 'XL', ARRAY['Rock'], 'Explosive color bursts over void black — Donwood''s most painterly work mirrors the album''s dynamic range from whisper to roar.', '5vkqYmiPBYLaalcmjujWxK', 15, 80, 45, '[]', 'approved'),
('Currents', 'Tame Impala', 'Robert Beatty', 'Illustration', 2015, 'Modular', ARRAY['Rock', 'Electronic'], 'Beatty''s swirling vortex of liquid chrome perfectly visualizes the album''s theme of unstoppable personal transformation.', '79dL7FLiJFOO0EoehUHQBv', 300, 50, 40, '[]', 'approved'),
