('SEIS', 'Mon Laferte', 'Mon Laferte', 'Illustration', 2021, 'Universal', ARRAY['Pop'], 'Laferte painted her own cover — a self-portrait that doubles as emotional autobiography, raw and unapologetically Latina.', '3EOGXDmeHGGlAFAIlagcDF', 350, 55, 40, '[]', 'approved'),
('El Mal Querer', 'Rosalía', 'Filip Custic', 'Photography', 2018, 'Columbia', ARRAY['Pop', 'Electronic'], 'Custic''s hyper-real, almost surgical aesthetic — red nails, clinical pose — announced a new visual language for flamenco''s future.', '355bjCHzRJztCzaG5Za4gq', 0, 70, 35, '[]', 'approved'),
('Nevermind', 'Nirvana', 'Kirk Weddle', 'Photography', 1991, 'DGC', ARRAY['Rock'], 'Weddle''s underwater baby shot became the defining image of the ''90s — raw, provocative, and impossible to forget.', '6okv1avxEgYSdc2JYy6ZEi', 200, 60, 45, '[]', 'approved'),
('IGOR', 'Tyler, the Creator', 'Felicia Tomasko', 'Photography', 2019, 'Columbia', ARRAY['Hip-hop'], 'The pink-wigged alter ego cover is as genre-bending as the music — pop art meets soul, styled to perfection.', '5zi7WsKlIiUXv09tbGLKsE', 340, 50, 55, '[]', 'approved'),
